body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello! This is Emily Green from Secure Auto Solutions. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Julia. Can you please provide me with the last four digits of your social security number for verification purposes?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, it's three two zero zero.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you. Now, could you also confirm your birthdate by sharing the day, month, and year separately?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: My birthdate is zero seven, zero five, one nine eight nine.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Julia, for providing that information. Is there anything specific you'd like assistance with today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm feeling sad about a recent security issue at the dealership.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I understand your concern. Thank you for sharing that with me, Julia. We will work together to address this. Your feedback is valuable.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for your time, Julia. If you have any more questions or concerns, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
